{"tid":889222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★包贏？】有市民稱相信股評人推介投資虛擬貨幣　回報半年挫九成","createTime":"2018-11-04T11:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T12:17:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c57380ce99ef24441148c4a4908a296259bea812","tid":889222,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBY96Dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBY96Dd.png&h=bbb44f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有政黨接獲多宗有關投資虛擬貨幣陷阱的投訴，發現投資者都因為一位股評人推介而決定投資，有人甚至因此借貸投資，但相關虛擬貨幣的回報率半年來大跌九成。<br />\n<br />\n投資者簽訂的合約中，有條款列明不可以在本港提出訴訟，所有法律行動要在英國進行。有執業律師認為條款苛刻，令投資者不敢循法律途徑追討損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426563-20181104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426563-20181104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=1ZBYsp%2FwIU%2BXG7hVFOcWV4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=37755ace\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426563-20181104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=67b54ba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426563-20181104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"145fcc2bc541baa1ae85df6bddd5be7ea6707b39","tid":889222,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:46:54.000Z","msg":"1478回水不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38b59c34fa79ee9bf6ee9332a61ac798b73ebd7","tid":889222,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"老貓買支股輸晒老綜，睇佢仆街最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}